{"tid":249443,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"呢度有無赤航仔？","createTime":"2017-05-19T09:59:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-22T12:32:16.000Z","uid":3527,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ee7dedf1e7bc31f6fd567ba7b61e570c35fcdbb6","tid":249443,"uid":3527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T09:59:04.000Z","msg":"全港唯一仲有軍事訓練嘅中學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以前啲赤航仔都操到好fit 好好J<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔似出面成班潺仔肥仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實係裡面生活係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啲體能係唔係真係操到好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果唔聽話又會點？會唔會罰體能以外嘅嘢？<br />\n同埋點解係航海學校但唔係跟皇家海軍嘅操法？要踏腳唔係拍腳？salute 唔係心口拉上手背向出？點解係外圍上手掌向出？<br />\n有無赤航仔入嚟講下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：以前有諗過入去讀，幾鍾意水上活動，但只收男仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a9b5ba341ea040a736984f02c1daf92d0c4d8f9","tid":249443,"uid":114097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T10:01:03.000Z","msg":"入面真係全部肥毒畢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有朋友喺入面讀緊"},{"pid":"95821a97111dc21477fb45c11ff01c94a8ba8677","tid":249443,"uid":3527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T10:07:54.000Z","msg":"仲有你地有幾多套制服？<br />\nAWD? 普通裇衫黑褲？運動服？Marching Band衫？水手裝？Guard 隊制服？<br />\n啲衫係要自己俾錢定有資助？<br />\n個膞頭又係點分？得普通乜都無同'撈'仔？有粒星又係代表咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ae316fda3d156f047388a2fb4e35303bdabd3bb","tid":249443,"uid":3527,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T10:12:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>入面真係全部肥毒畢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有朋友喺入面讀緊</blockquote><br />\n可能呢幾年貼近主流學校，無太多所謂不良學生入去，我見啲宣傳片真係多咗好多肥毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聽講以前係好多無學校收或者管唔掂或者有經濟困難嘅入去讀，比較想知以前啲人會點管，係唔係真係仲辛苦過入男童院<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"943d76d24d4bff875cafd39fc6220babfe260fd6","tid":249443,"uid":3527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T10:26:12.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94b7dbdc27b74493fdd679cd2387e7f4c5c347d3","tid":249443,"uid":3527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T10:39:12.000Z","msg":"呢度竟然無赤航仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e965bef0382ea78588473463c6ed55dfc9667ed0","tid":249443,"uid":35379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T10:51:21.000Z","msg":"龍舟比賽遇過赤航~<br />\n唔係話好大隻~肥仔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"038252b955cb02578aa588ee1c661f422707cc2c","tid":249443,"uid":2260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T13:53:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"81766b000c9e7826b1bb472f01f0288eec75722b","tid":249443,"uid":3527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T15:45:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>識一個赤航仔...玩開船...幾大隻幾好J<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你果個係幾耐之前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家果啲好似樓上話齋好多肥仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0522bc8c7e40c2874b11059ebeab73e647d4a7d9","tid":249443,"uid":2260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T15:50:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1025ef007455030d1fb7f4694e0edd798f14a622","tid":249443,"uid":3527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T16:32:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>識一個赤航仔...玩開船...幾大隻幾好J<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你果個係幾耐之前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家果啲好似樓上話齋好多肥仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n上年grad<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢有無講過裡面生活係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解講咁耐都無真赤航仔回post 嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d260bc7cca720968c95e1e6a560f65abd49856cc","tid":249443,"uid":4625,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T16:33:37.000Z","msg":"赤航10個有7個都on9"},{"pid":"9b27d6a17c29bea9861d000dcb352bcf55a1da17","tid":249443,"uid":2333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T16:46:05.000Z","msg":"出到黎多數撈偏 同做社會底層<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ba03da4654352306500b8d13185a86e57ec2623","tid":249443,"uid":3527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T16:54:24.000Z","msg":"樓上果啲係偏見定真係識人係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n老老柒柒赤航仔可能學術方面唔勁，但好少見佢地上新聞，咩自殺犯法都唔覺有（入去前好跩嘅唔出奇，但果時都未算赤航仔）<br />\n到底樓上啲言論係根據啲咩講？"},{"pid":"5d047c323358423b6fd7403cea7a095b37c5f593","tid":249443,"uid":77837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T16:54:28.000Z","msg":"Thank you Sir! 唔該同學!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c8b1479c342b3453f979e2b462e3075c37fe857","tid":249443,"uid":2260,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T20:17:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2b92b517d277757cf4733408f3c8635c080a3f5d","tid":249443,"uid":19722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T20:24:59.000Z","msg":"一級都唔知仲有冇50人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d68dad97cf5876f0a787555e9de5c728f5d5e50","tid":249443,"uid":79502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T05:06:08.000Z","msg":"學校主要分玩水，樂隊，廚房三大方向，亦有少數乖仔讀書(果個係我&gt;&lt;)"},{"pid":"6d690015586989f71cce258f07eb28d4fbf6d843","tid":249443,"uid":79502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T05:19:39.000Z","msg":"外人傳聞入面好恐怖好多打架 ，<br />\n其實係真，不過係好多年前，呢一兩年已經冇乜，因為學校開始改革，社會講緊人權，所以所謂大佬都唔敢亂黎，同埋隔離就係赤柱警署。<br />\n學校最大懲罰叫做 開RB ，星期六Full day幫學校做野， <br />\n總結：赤航已經唔係以前咁"},{"pid":"8d91511f109a2e52e67d949cca1b72907b2b7308","tid":249443,"uid":62226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T05:22:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>入面真係全部肥毒畢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有朋友喺入面讀緊</blockquote><br />\n可能呢幾年貼近主流學校，無太多所謂不良學生入去，我見啲宣傳片真係多咗好多肥毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聽講以前係好多無學校收或者管唔掂或者有經濟困難嘅入去讀，比較想知以前啲人會點管，係唔係真係仲辛苦過入男童院<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n而家社會都少左mk仔古惑仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e674a44abfb339a02b60eece4719ff4b74544b6c","tid":249443,"uid":4155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T05:33:58.000Z","msg":"以前入面就一係mk仔，一係就毒撚<br />\n毒撚就好撚慘，mk仔連老師都恰可想而知毒撚係點<br />\n以前仲有單俾人玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n總結：狗都唔讀"},{"pid":"1c479fc1fdfa81b9c1eb2a4169324bf1b7eb06e8","tid":249443,"uid":4625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T07:08:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓上果啲係偏見定真係識人係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n老老柒柒赤航仔可能學術方面唔勁，但好少見佢地上新聞，咩自殺犯法都唔覺有（入去前好跩嘅唔出奇，但果時都未算赤航仔）<br />\n到底樓上啲言論係根據啲咩講？</blockquote><br />\n可能我慘d,識親既赤航仔讀完又係咁讀緊又係咁"},{"pid":"0fdb5ba630eefd1f5c7af918166f9e3dfc285205","tid":249443,"uid":54528,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T07:13:04.000Z","msg":"呢到香港呀, 讀呢D學校9成9都係垃圾"},{"pid":"2774e10c96267e654c65c82283eb6c5f5a603517","tid":249443,"uid":28190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s